r the next one, so we had a job all the time. After all the hay or corn had been cut, well, of course, he gave us other jobs, like digging up beans, and all sorts of things. But we used to be in the field about 8 in the morning 'till 8 at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12584100 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16144818\charrsid16144818 At 7 years old?
