 backwards and forwards to whatever rookery they belonged to. We used to have to wait 'till about 4 in the af
ternoon when it got dark. We used to go Christmas Day and Boxing Day, and Sundays, just the same. I did that for 4 Christmases running. So then, of course, we used to go along and have a real old good time then.
